  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients aged &gt; 18 years

          -  acquisition of written informed consent

          -  Major abdominal surgery (major gastrointestinal surgery: DCP, gastrectomy, Miles,
             emicolectomy; gynecologic surgery: oncologic surgery) Surgery times ≥ 3 hours

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Absolute contraindication to CVC placement

          -  pregnant women

          -  hepatic surgery

          -  laparoscopic surgery

          -  Major vascular surgery

          -  Dialysis treatment and kidney transplant surgery

          -  Severe heart failure (EF ≤ 35%)

          -  Emergency surgery
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
